Text: Good quality but this isn't the whole thing, just a half hour teaser. The entire thing is 90 minutes.
This was a really cool Documentary, I watch it this weekend on my Dish TV, crazy to think what might be out there........

I liked this because I like believing there is more to this world than we are aware of, but as a documentary, it's not so good. It's over-hyped and exaggerated in many ways. But still, it provides some interesting theories if you believe in stuff like mermaids or have an open mind about this kind of things.
